text: Feed Me () is a 2013 Chinese drama film directed by Yang Yazhou and Yang Bo. It was shown at the Montreal World Film Festival on August 29, 2013 and was released in China on May 22, 2015. ==Cast== *Yu Nan *Tao Zeru *Lin Hao *Vivian Wu ==Reception== The film won the Prix de l’innovation (Innovation award) at the 2013 Montreal World Film Festival.
